Package: pwpldis
Title: Discrete piecewise power-law model
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nixon", "Jerez Lillo", , "njerezlillo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8750-969"))
Description: This package provides tools for fitting the piecewise discrete 
             power-law model. It includes maximum likelihood estimation methods
             and a bootstrapping procedure to correct the bias of the estimators.
